	    <h2>skos-label</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-12">
		    <p>
		      Used as attribute to emit the preferred label of a concept. The lang
		      attribute of the directive element is read and set accordingly. If
		      no label of the required language exists, another language is selected.
		    </p>
		    <p>
		      <ul>
				    <li><span skos-label="sampleConcept" lang="de" class="show-lang"/></li>
				    <li><span skos-label="sampleConcept" lang="en" class="show-lang"/></li>
				    <li><span skos-label="sampleConcept" class="show-lang"/></li>
				    <li><span skos-label="sampleConcept" lang="fr" class="show-lang"/></li>
		      </ul>
		    </p>
      </div>
